    - Enables full VM state preservation during snapshots
  * New Feature: Automatic Multipath Configuration
    - postinst: Automatically adds NetApp device config to /etc/multipath.conf
    - Skips if existing NetApp configuration detected (manual setup respected)
    - Creates backup before modifying multipath.conf
